<h3><a id="user-content-helmets" class="anchor" href="#helmets" aria-hidden="true"><span class="octicon octicon-link"></span></a>Helmets</h3>

<p>Everyone should wear a helmet while riding. DOT fits and gives away the official New York City bicycle helmet at events throughout the city. Call 311 to schedule a fitting. In order to receive a helmet you must: be present, learn how to properly fit and wear a helmet, and sign a waiver (a parent or legal guardian must sign for children under 18).</p>

